694static const HashTable JSNavigatorPrototypeTable = { 40, 127, true, JSNavigator::info(), JSNavigatorPrototypeTableValues, JSNavigatorPrototypeTableIndex };
695const ClassInfo JSNavigatorPrototype::s_info = { "Navigator", &Base::s_info, &JSNavigatorPrototypeTable, nullptr, CREATE_METHOD_TABLE(JSNavigatorPrototype) };
696
697void JSNavigatorPrototype::finishCreation(VM& vm)
698{
699 Base::finishCreation(vm);
700 reifyStaticProperties(vm, JSNavigator::info(), JSNavigatorPrototypeTableValues, *this);
701 JSC_TO_STRING_TAG_WITHOUT_TRANSITION();
702}
703
704const ClassInfo JSNavigator::s_info = { "Navigator", &Base::s_info, nullptr, nullptr, CREATE_METHOD_TABLE(JSNavigator) };
705
706JSNavigator::JSNavigator(Structure* structure, JSDOMGlobalObject& globalObject, Ref<Navigator>&& impl)
707 : JSDOMWrapper<Navigator>(structure, globalObject, WTFMove(impl))
708{
709}
710
711void JSNavigator::finishCreation(VM& vm)
712{
713 Base::finishCreation(vm);
714 ASSERT(inherits(vm, info()));
715
716 static_assert(!std::is_base_of<ActiveDOMObject, Navigator>::value, "Interface is not marked as [ActiveDOMObject] even though implementation class subclasses ActiveDOMObject.");
717
718}
719
720JSObject* JSNavigator::createPrototype(VM& vm, JSDOMGlobalObject& globalObject)
721{
722 return JSNavigatorPrototype::create(vm, &globalObject, JSNavigatorPrototype::createStructure(vm, &globalObject, globalObject.objectPrototype()));
723}
724
725JSObject* JSNavigator::prototype(VM& vm, JSDOMGlobalObject& globalObject)
726{
727 return getDOMPrototype<JSNavigator>(vm, globalObject);
728}
729
730JSValue JSNavigator::getConstructor(VM& vm, const JSGlobalObject* globalObject)
731{
732 return getDOMConstructor<JSNavigatorDOMConstructor, DOMConstructorID::Navigator>(vm, *jsCast<const JSDOMGlobalObject*>(globalObject));
733}
734
735void JSNavigator::destroy(JSC::JSCell* cell)
736{
737 JSNavigator* thisObject = static_cast<JSNavigator*>(cell);
738 thisObject->JSNavigator::~JSNavigator();
739}

741JSC_DEFINE_CUSTOM_GETTER(jsNavigatorConstructor, (JSGlobalObject* lexicalGlobalObject, EncodedJSValue thisValue, PropertyName))
742{
743 VM& vm = JSC::getVM(lexicalGlobalObject);
744 auto throwScope = DECLARE_THROW_SCOPE(vm);
745 auto* prototype = jsDynamicCast<JSNavigatorPrototype*>(vm, JSValue::decode(thisValue));
746 if (UNLIKELY(!prototype))
747 return throwVMTypeError(lexicalGlobalObject, throwScope);
748 return JSValue::encode(JSNavigator::getConstructor(JSC::getVM(lexicalGlobalObject), prototype->globalObject()));
749}

1349 RELEASE_AND_RETURN(throwScope, JSValue::encode(toJS<IDLPromise<IDLUndefined>>(*lexicalGlobalObject, *castedThis->globalObject(), throwScope, [&]() -> decltype(auto) { return impl.share(document, WTFMove(shareData), WTFMove(promise)); })));
1350}
1351
1352JSC_DEFINE_HOST_FUNCTION(jsNavigatorPrototypeFunction_share, (JSGlobalObject* lexicalGlobalObject, CallFrame* callFrame))
1353{
1354 return IDLOperationReturningPromise<JSNavigator>::call<jsNavigatorPrototypeFunction_shareBody>(*lexicalGlobalObject, *callFrame, "share");
1355}
1356
1357JSC::IsoSubspace* JSNavigator::subspaceForImpl(JSC::VM& vm)
1358{
1359 auto& clientData = *static_cast<JSVMClientData*>(vm.clientData);
1360 auto& spaces = clientData.subspaces();
1361 if (auto* space = spaces.m_subspaceForNavigator.get())
1362 return space;
1363 static_assert(std::is_base_of_v<JSC::JSDestructibleObject, JSNavigator> || !JSNavigator::needsDestruction);
1364 if constexpr (std::is_base_of_v<JSC::JSDestructibleObject, JSNavigator>)
1365 spaces.m_subspaceForNavigator = makeUnique<IsoSubspace> ISO_SUBSPACE_INIT(vm.heap, vm.destructibleObjectHeapCellType.get(), JSNavigator);
1366 else
1367 spaces.m_subspaceForNavigator = makeUnique<IsoSubspace> ISO_SUBSPACE_INIT(vm.heap, vm.cellHeapCellType.get(), JSNavigator);
1368 auto* space = spaces.m_subspaceForNavigator.get();
1369IGNORE_WARNINGS_BEGIN("unreachable-code")
1370IGNORE_WARNINGS_BEGIN("tautological-compare")
1371 void (*myVisitOutputConstraint)(JSC::JSCell*, JSC::SlotVisitor&) = JSNavigator::visitOutputConstraints;
1372 void (*jsCellVisitOutputConstraint)(JSC::JSCell*, JSC::SlotVisitor&) = JSC::JSCell::visitOutputConstraints;
1373 if (myVisitOutputConstraint != jsCellVisitOutputConstraint)
1374 clientData.outputConstraintSpaces().append(space);
1375IGNORE_WARNINGS_END
1376IGNORE_WARNINGS_END
1377 return space;
1378}

1411bool JSNavigatorOwner::isReachableFromOpaqueRoots(JSC::Handle<JSC::Unknown> handle, void*, AbstractSlotVisitor& visitor, const char** reason)
1412{
1413 auto* jsNavigator = jsCast<JSNavigator*>(handle.slot()->asCell());
1414 auto* root = WTF::getPtr(jsNavigator->wrapped().window());
1415 if (!root)
1416 return false;
1417 if (UNLIKELY(reason))
1418 *reason = "Reachable from Window";
1419 return visitor.containsOpaqueRoot(root);
1420}

1422void JSNavigatorOwner::finalize(JSC::Handle<JSC::Unknown> handle, void* context)
1423{
1424 auto* jsNavigator = static_cast<JSNavigator*>(handle.slot()->asCell());
1425 auto& world = *static_cast<DOMWrapperWorld*>(context);
1426 uncacheWrapper(world, &jsNavigator->wrapped(), jsNavigator);
1427}

1437
1438JSC::JSValue toJSNewlyCreated(JSC::JSGlobalObject*, JSDOMGlobalObject* globalObject, Ref<Navigator>&& impl)
1439{
1440
1441#if ENABLE(BINDING_INTEGRITY)
1442 const void* actualVTablePointer = getVTablePointer(impl.ptr());
1443#if PLATFORM(WIN)
1444 void* expectedVTablePointer = __identifier("??_7Navigator@WebCore@@6B@");
1445#else
1446 void* expectedVTablePointer = &_ZTVN7WebCore9NavigatorE[2];
1447#endif
1448
1449 // If this fails Navigator does not have a vtable, so you need to add the
1450 // ImplementationLacksVTable attribute to the interface definition
1451 static_assert(std::is_polymorphic<Navigator>::value, "Navigator is not polymorphic");
1452
1453 // If you hit this assertion you either have a use after free bug, or
1454 // Navigator has subclasses. If Navigator has subclasses that get passed
1455 // to toJS() we currently require Navigator you to opt out of binding hardening
1456 // by adding the SkipVTableValidation attribute to the interface IDL definition
1457 RELEASE_ASSERT(actualVTablePointer == expectedVTablePointer);
1458#endif
1459 return createWrapper<Navigator>(globalObject, WTFMove(impl));
1460}
